    <Name>Paladin</Name>
    <Description>A Paladin is a warrior that trades some melee power for the ability
to cast divine spells. The Paladin often has the best saving throws of
any character, gains immunity to fear and disease, and may also serve as
backup healers for short encounters. They also have passive auras that
aid their party members when facing evil creatures. Paladins make great
defensive characters, but can easily perform well in an offensive role
with weapons. The primary attributes of Paladins are Wisdom (for
spellcasting and spell points) and Charisma (for higher saves and
increasing the effectiveness of their unique abilities). Strength and
Constitution should not be discarded, of course, as the Paladin is a
martial class.</Description>
